This repository contains the Lahzo Internal Design System, including the Lahzo
name, logos, brand fonts (Beirut Display) and visual language. It is intended
for internal use within the organization.

Internal teams may use these assets to build Lahzo internal tools. Redistribution
of the brand assets (logos, Beirut Display font, theme) outside the organization
is not permitted without written permission.

Third-party assets retain their own licenses:
  - Instrument Sans, IBM Plex Mono — SIL Open Font License 1.1 (loaded from Google Fonts)
  - Phosphor Icons — MIT License (https://github.com/phosphor-icons/homepage)
